dcterms:description: The DDSM dataset contains mammogram images that were digitized by different scanners with varying resolutions. For data consistency, mammograms scanned by Howtek 960 were selected, resulting in a total of 1,088 regions of interest (ROIs) which were either malignant or benign masses, annotated by radiologists.
dcterms:title: DDSM (Digital Database for Screening Mammography)
